Version 1.3

    Item Addition: Added a 50% chance for Champions to receive items.
    Necromancer Update: Removed turn-based surfaces created by Necromancer transformations.
    Follower Restrictions: Prevented potential followers from transforming into Champions.
    Boss Restrictions: Disallowed specific bosses (Ketheric, Ethel, Skeletal Dragon, Netherbrain, Raphael) from transforming into Champions.
    Improved Events: Enhanced party table calculation events for better gameplay mechanics.

Version 1.2

    Transformation Fix: Ensures that entities won't re-evaluate and transform multiple times once their health drops below the transformation threshold.
    Compatibility Fixes:
        Resolved incompatibility with the "Enemy Stats" mod.
        Resolved incompatibility with the "Absolute Wrath" mod.
